OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FA teacher accused of the murder and
OL,8,Fsexual abuse of an adopted baby boy
OL,9,Fhas denied he used him as a
OL,10,F"plaything" for his "own amusement and
OL,11,Fgratification".
OL,13,FJamie Varley, 37, is alleged to have
OL,14,Fregularly sexually, physically and
OL,15,Femotionally abused Preston Davey, 13
OL,16,Fmonths, whom he had adopted with his
OL,17,Fpartner John McGowan-Fazakerley.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@KO]rD@UOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
