PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FPreston, described previously as
OL,8,Fhappy, healthy and "bubbly", began
OL,9,Fliving with the defendants at their
OL,10,Fhome in Blackpool, Lancashire, on 1
OL,11,FApril 2023, Preston Crown Court has
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FBut the prosecution say that in the
OL,15,Fnext four months before his death on
OL,16,F27 July he was routinely ill-treated,
OL,17,Fhad indecent images and videos taken
OL,18,Fof him, and was sexually abused and
OL,19,Fphysically assaulted, suffering 40
OL,20,Ftraumatic injuries found at a post-
OL,21,Fmortem examination.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
