PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FIn cross-examination on 27 May,
OL,8,Fprosecutor Peter Wright KC said to
OL,9,FVarley: "This little boy was your
OL,10,Fplaything, wasn't he?"
OL,12,FVarley replied: "You are wrong."
OL,14,FMr Wright said: "And you routinely
OL,15,Fabused him."
OL,17,FVarley repeated: "You are wrong."
OL,19,FMr Wright said: "For your own
OL,20,Famusement and gratification."
OL,26,@qD@IOUrD@VO]tD@QOUtD@`O]vD@QOUwD@LO]yD@
OL,26,AROUyD@aO]{D@QOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
