PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,F"Incorrect," said Varley.
OL,9,FThe prosecutor went on: "All of this
OL,10,Fin a space of less than four months.
OL,11,FIt went from him coming into your home
OL,12,Fand leaving it dead, didn't it?"
OL,14,FThe defendant said: "He did pass away
OL,15,Fin our care, yes."
OL,17,FPreston was taken to hospital having
OL,18,Fsuffered a collapse and cardiac
OL,19,Farrest, allegedly after a sexual
OL,20,Fassault by Varley.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]qD@YOUtD@`O]vD@UOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
