PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FVarley told police he had briefly left
OL,8,Fthe child in the bath and when he
OL,9,Freturned he was off his bath seat and
OL,10,Fsubmerged.
OL,12,FBut a post-mortem examination ruled
OL,13,Fout drowning and found multiple non-
OL,14,Faccidental, internal and external
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,FThe cause of Preston's death was found
OL,18,Fto be acute upper airways obstruction
OL,19,Fby either smothering or an object or
OL,20,Fobjects inserted into his mouth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
