PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FVarley said he had never sexually
OL,8,Fassaulted Preston and he denied Mr
OL,9,FWright's suggestion that he had
OL,10,Fblocked Preston's airways more than
OL,11,Fonce.
OL,13,FMr Wright said: "And on the day he
OL,14,Fdied such was the obstruction of his
OL,15,Fupper airways, caused by you, that he
OL,16,Fperished. You killed him."
OL,18,FVarley said: "I have not."
OL,26,@uD@QOUxD@ZO]zD@NOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
