PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FVarley said: "I would be more
OL,8,Fintelligent, sir, if that was the
OL,9,Fcase. I genuinely thought he had
OL,10,Fdrowned."
OL,12,FIn suggesting to Varley there were
OL,13,Fnumerous inconsistencies in the
OL,14,Faccounts he gave at the hospital and
OL,15,Fto police, Mr Wright said: "You have
OL,16,Fbeen making it up from the start to
OL,17,Fthe end, haven't you?"
OL,19,FVarley said: "I would say it was a
OL,20,Fvery traumatic day, sir.
OL,26,@oD@NOUrD@IO]wD@\OUyD@VO]{D@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
