OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,F"It was the worst day of our lives. I
OL,8,Fcould hardly speak that day. I was all
OL,9,Fover."
OL,11,FMr Wright said: "I am going to suggest
OL,12,Fthat when you got to the hospital your
OL,13,Fapparent state of distress was a
OL,14,Fcomplete charade."
OL,16,FVarley replied: "That's not true."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@FO]sD@QOUvD@RO]xD@QOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
