OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779905470
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FMr Wright said: "And your inability
OL,8,Fthen to be able to settle and answer
OL,9,Fquestions was because you were working
OL,10,Fovertime to come up with an
OL,11,Fexplanation for what you had done to
OL,12,Fhim?"
OL,14,F"That is not true," said Varley.
OL,16,FMr Wright said: "Buying time to try to
OL,17,Fthink of a way out."
OL,19,FVarley said: "That's not correct."
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@EO]vD@AOUvD@SO]xD@QOUyD@TO]{D@
