OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FThe defendant denied that later police
OL,8,Fexamination of images on his phone
OL,9,Fdemonstrated he had repeatedly ill-
OL,10,Ftreated the child,
OL,12,FMr Wright put it to Varley that by
OL,13,FJuly 2023 his partner also had a
OL,14,Fsexual interest in Preston.
OL,16,FVarley said: "John and I don't have a
OL,17,Fsexual interest in children."
OL,19,FMr Wright said: "That little boy was
OL,20,Fthe plaything of both of you, wasn't
OL,21,Fhe?"
OL,26,@xD@NOUyD@]O]{D@QOU}D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
