OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,F"No," he said.
OL,9,FMr Wright said: "And you each ill-
OL,10,Ftreated him, didn't you?"
OL,12,FVarley said: "No we did not."
OL,14,FMr Wright said: "You were obsessed
OL,15,Fwith this boy in a sexual nature,
OL,16,Fweren't you?"
OL,18,FThe defendant replied: "You are wrong."
