OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder denied he
OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FVarley denied he was "struggling to
OL,8,Fcope" with Preston, would "lose his
OL,9,Ftemper" and had physically abused the
OL,10,Fboy.
OL,12,FHe said: "I would give anything for
OL,13,Fthat boy."
OL,15,FMr Wright said: "You were abusing this
OL,16,Fboy, weren't you?"
OL,18,FVarley said: "No, we were not. I just
OL,19,Fknow he was in a safe and loving home.
OL,21,F"He loved us and we loved him."
