OL,4,Cused baby as 'plaything' for 'own
OL,5,Camusement'
OL,7,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,8,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,9,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,10,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,11,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,12,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,13,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,14,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,15,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,17,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, 32, denies
OL,18,Fallowing the death of a child, three
OL,19,Fcounts of child cruelty and one count
OL,20,Fof the sexual assault of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
